data.description: This home has the cutest curb appeal and is ready for its new owner! Spacious living room and dining area. Plenty of windows to let in natural light.  Primary bedroom with updated ensuite bathroom. In house laundry room with washer and dryer hookup. Home features a sunroom and enclosed garage for flex spaces, perfect for entertaining.  Nicely sized rooms.  New roof , new front door, and several new windows. Large backyard that's fully fenced. Walking distance to Ki Mexico, Lowder's Baking Co., Marilynn's Place, Sweet Glaze Donuts, and Doc's Sandwich Shop! Minutes away from Querbes Golf Course and the Highland Parade Route!
